    caption: [Interaction of a PTB domain with a P –Tyr residue in a partner protein. (PDB ID 1SHC) The PTB domain is represented as a blue surface contour. The P –Tyr residue of the partner protein (red) projects into a binding pocket in the PTB domain and is held firmly by multiple noncovalent interactions. 12.5 Multivalent Adaptor Proteins and Membrane Rafts 461],
